fast-track as they call it.

00:23:14.390 --> 00:23:17.910
So usually what happens is, you
get a contract from your publisher

00:23:17.910 --> 00:23:20.140
and I told you I'm
a Scholastic author.

00:23:20.140 --> 00:23:23.750
