year to 18 months to write

00:23:23.750 --> 00:23:27.800
and then they get a year to produce
the book so it's really a two

00:23:27.800 --> 00:23:30.320
to two and a half year process.

00:23:30.320 --> 00:23:31.620
Some books take longer.

00:23:31.620 --> 00:23:32.920
Some books are shorter.

00:23:32.920 --> 00:23:35.110
This one, we wrote it in a year

00:23:35.110 --> 00:23:38.320
and it was produced
within the two years so.

00:23:38.320 --> 00:23:39.730
It takes a full year though.

00:23:39.730 --> 00:23:45.380
