first draft and do my edits.

00:23:45.380 --> 00:23:48.380
I may do a thousand edits on my
first draft and then I send it

00:23:48.380 --> 00:23:50.240
to my editor and he
sends back comments.

00:23:50.240 --> 00:23:54.850
